Package: rctsimple
Type: Package
Title: Simple Analysis of Outcome Data from Randomised Controlled Trials (RCTs)
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jim", "Vine", email = "code@jimvine.co.uk", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for analysing data from randomised controlled trials
    (RCTs), supporting both aggregate and raw (participant-level) data. This
    package focuses on calculating some simple statistics and presenting them
    in a simple fashion.
